{"tid":1333391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府賑災基金撥款助內地災民 香港電台","createTime":"2019-07-19T16:18:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T17:19:18.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5e5ba5f9720da89397c2457d0a3170c7d78d8770","tid":1333391,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:18:29.000Z","msg":"2019年7月19日<br />\n<br />\n政府從賑災基金批出4,542,000元予愛德基金會（香港），賑濟廣西壯族自治區和江西省水災災民。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n撥款按賑災基金諮詢委員會的建議批出，為災民提供食物、棉被和衞生用品，幫助他們早日回復正常生活。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n愛德基金會（香港）完成賑災計劃後，須向委員會呈交評估報告和經審核帳目，確保撥款用於指定用途。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/07/20190719/20190719_171420_135.html?type=ticker%3Cbr%20/%3E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news.gov.hk%2Fchi%2F2019%2F07%2F20190719%2F20190719_171420_135.html%3Ftype%3Dticker%253Cbr%2520%2F%253E&d=6pEOCw3Iqoz%2FZ73NBW83J36wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=1e8665b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.news.gov.hk/chi/2019/07/20190719/20190719_171420_135.html?type=ticker%3Cbr%20/%3E</a>"},{"pid":"37cb067513d915accc431eb0ac8348a8cf95034c","tid":1333391,"uid":125193,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:19:09.000Z","msg":"痴撚線，又要香港人埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620265445fd9f2b5c77a570f3572d2d01dbb8194","tid":1333391,"uid":125193,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:20:19.000Z","msg":"大陸咁撚強大 洗撚香港三線城市幫助咩"},{"pid":"64864027097581be23dc71fdc01294da96f44e03","tid":1333391,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">請廣傳</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"8f9c51ebc4fb4044a4da903838bc053ad92ff2bf","tid":1333391,"uid":125193,"like":0